OL,3,CBBC must take quicker action when
OL,4,Cstaff step out of line, report says
OL,6,FIt comes following former footballer
OL,7,FJermaine Jenas being sacked in 2024
OL,8,Ffrom The One Show after he admitted
OL,9,Fsending inappropriate messages to
OL,10,Ffemale colleagues, and concerns voiced
OL,11,Fby Strictly Come Dancing contestants
OL,12,Fabout the duty of care on the series.
OL,14,FLast year also saw Gregg Wallace step
OL,15,Faway from hosting BBC cooking
OL,16,Fcompetition MasterChef after
OL,17,Fhistorical complaints came to light,
OL,18,Fand the show's production company,
OL,19,FBanijay UK, launched an external
OL,20,Finvestigation.
