OL,3,CBBC must take quicker action when
OL,4,Cstaff step out of line, report says
OL,6,FThe report will be published at 11am
OL,7,Fon Monday, after staff attend a call
OL,8,Fwith BBC chairman Samir Shah, director-
OL,9,Fgeneral Tim Davie and Baroness Helena
OL,10,FKennedy, chairwoman of the board of
OL,11,Fthe newly created Creative Industries
OL,12,FIndependent Standards Authority
OL,13,F(CIISA).
OL,15,FIn February 2024, the BBC apologised
OL,16,Fto the family of the young person at
OL,17,Fthe centre of the Edwards furore, and
OL,18,Fa report found a need for "greater
OL,19,Fconsistency" in how complaints at the
OL,20,Fcorporation are processed.
