OL,6,FThat same year, the BBC guidelines on
OL,7,Frelationships in the workplace were
OL,8,Fupdated.
OL,10,FThey warn staff that using "celebrity
OL,11,Fstatus" to influence people to make a
OL,12,Fdecision in your favour is an "abuse
OL,13,Fof power", and highlighted concerns
OL,14,Fover "signs or evidence of potential
OL,15,Fgrooming".
OL,17,FFollowing the update being published,
OL,18,FEdwards admitted a separate incident
OL,19,Fto the 2023 BBC complaint.
