OL,12,Fpresenter's conviction has damaged the
OL,13,Freputation of the BBC, and the
OL,14,Fcorporation is seeking the estimated
OL,15,F#200,000 salary Edwards was paid
OL,16,Fbetween his arrest and leaving the
OL,17,Fcorporation in April 2024.
